macro.title: Mortgage rates could move higher despite a Fed cut
macro.what: While the Federal Reserve is expected to deliver another interest rate cut on Wednesday, mortgage rates aren’t likely to move much lower
macro.why: Rates & inflation shape discount rates and housing affordability.
macro.market: Lower rates support demand/valuations; higher rates pressure builders/REITs and slow transactions.

macro.why: Rates & inflation shape discount rates and housing affordability.
